# No built-in AI provider — BYOK only. Configure providers in Settings → Advanced.

# ─── Composio API Key ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get your API key at https://dashboard.composio.dev/settings
# This replaces the need to set up individual OAuth apps for each service.
# Composio handles auth for Linear, Atlassian, Trello, Airtable, Notion,
# Slack, GitHub, Google Workspace, HubSpot, Asana, Dropbox, and more.
#
# COMPOSIO_API_KEY=your_composio_api_key